{"type":null,"faqId":19368,"title":"4G 常见问题","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-family:Frutiger Next Com;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:13pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>为什么我的 </span><span class=\"s1\">4G</span><span> 手机经常会没有 </span><span class=\"s1\">4G</span><span> 信号，仅显示 </span><span class=\"s1\">3G</span><span> 或 </span><span class=\"s1\">G</span><span>？</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>中国移动 </span><span class=\"s1\">4G</span><span> 网络处于建设、优化阶段，目前还不能覆盖所有区域。在中国移动 </span><span class=\"s1\">4G</span><span> 网络未覆盖区域，您可以通过 </span><span class=\"s1\">3G</span><span> 或 </span><span class=\"s1\">2G</span><span> 网络来上网。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>我的卡开通了 4G 套餐，为什么没有 4G 信号？</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，您可以打开通知面板，检查 </span><span class=\"s1\">4G</span><span> 开关是否打开。如果未打开，请点击 </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=64265\" style=\"width:0.22986111in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，启用 </span><span class=\"s1\">4G</span><span> 数据业务。如果还是没有 </span><span class=\"s1\">4G</span><span> 信号，您可以拨打 </span><span class=\"s1\">10086</span><span> 咨询您所在区域是否覆盖 </span><span class=\"s1\">4G</span><span> 网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>为什么我的 </span><span class=\"s1\">4G</span><span> 速度没有宣传的那么快？</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>实际速率可能会受到 </span><span class=\"s1\">4G</span><span> 信号强度、无线电干扰等现场环境以及您所访问的服务器带宽等的限制，有可能无法达到理论速度，但是相对于 </span><span class=\"s1\">3G</span><span> 的网络速度会有明显的提升。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2509","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422608225000,"seriesProductName":"G628-TL00","visitedTimes":116,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}